						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">mic_ wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Getting an SPC700 mode into ca65 would help. </div><br />WLA-DX has supported the SPC700 for a long time.<br /></div>
